snippet.title: Recording Academy / GRAMMYs
snippet.description: The Recording Academy represents the voices of performers, songwriters, producers, engineers, and all music professionals. Dedicated to ensuring the recording arts remain a thriving part of our shared cultural heritage, the Academy honors music's history while investing in its future through the GRAMMY Museum, advocates on behalf of music creators, supports music people in times of need through MusiCares, and celebrates artistic excellence through the GRAMMY Awards.

snippet.title: Sussan Mourad
snippet.description:
Hi Bestie!! Follow for all the CELEBRI-TEA & Entertainment News you need to know! ☕️ Join us! Love you! ❤️🥰

Welcome! I cover everything happening in entertainment and celebrity news, up to the minute!

I stay across all social platforms, celebrities, entertainment news articles and blogs (so you don't have to!) & bring you accurate, speedy & entertaining news updates that I produce, host & shoot myself. Any clips incorporated into my news videos, where I also always appear as a host, are included with a storyline and commentary & may also be part of a critical review and/or reaction.  

Any videos where I don't appear as a host are videos created & edited by me using cap-cut editing software. These videos comprise a selection of images I source and then create a video in capcut with text & carefully selected music that together create a storyline and commentary. If I'm not in the video as host its intentional for compelling story-telling but always a video created & edited by me.❤️

snippet.title: Rayvanny
snippet.description:
Raymond Shaban Mwakyusa (born 22 August 1993), better known by his stage name Rayvanny is a Tanzanian singer, songwriter, and The CEO of the Record label known as NEXT LEVEL MUSIC.

Rayvanny emerged in the spotlight with his debut song "Kwetu", which introduced him to the world. Later on, he released he grabbed attention with his hit song featuring Diamond Platnumz titled "Tetema" which grabbed different charts Worldwide. 

Rayvanny was mentioned by MTV Base among "Acts To Look Out For" in 2017 and also won Viewer's Choice Best New International Artist on BET Awards 2017.

Rayvanny has been the first AFRICAN ARTIST to perform at MTV EMA shows in late of 2021 with MALUMA, and he also  was the. first East African artist to win DIAFA AWARDS in late of 2022.

un cofre del tesoro que contiene los recuerdos más preciados del dúo musical FANTABEAT (Andrea Buranello & Fujiko Mine).
Las imágenes detrás de escena y los momentos que quedaron grabados en el corazón.
El concepto del inexorable paso del tiempo siempre nos ha fascinado:
especialmente Fujiko Mine quien siempre ha preferido vivir en mundos paralelos antes que enfrentar la realidad de tener que elegir entre la razón y el corazón.
Después de todo, todos viajamos juntos en el tiempo.
Y sólo nos queda hacer lo mejor que podemos para disfrutar de este increíble viaje.
La música nos salvó a los dos: nos dio ternura, complicidad y gran atención el uno hacia el otro.
¡Porque nadie está preparado para el amor, ni para lo que vendrá!

snippet.title: Study With G2 Sir
snippet.description:
Dear students,
हमने प्रतियोगी परीक्षाओं से जुडी अपनी तैयारी , रणनीति और शिक्षा को बेहतर बनाने के लिए Study With G2 Sir यूटयूब चैनल की शुरुआत की है | इस चैनल में हम प्रतियोगी परीक्षाओं से जुडे हर  टॉपिक को सम्पूर्ण तथ्यों के साथ पढ़ायेगें जिससे आपकी तैयारी की रणनीति और भी बेहतर होगी । वीडियो देखने के लिए हमारे चैनल को सब्सक्राइब करें।

Some lines of student:-
लाइफ में कभी हार मत मानो, हमेशा चलते रहो और जिंदगी के पथ पर आगे बढ़ते रहिए , जरूरी नहीं कि सफल होने के लिए एक कोचिंग ही होनी चाहिए, ये भी जरूरी नहीं कि सफल होने के लिए कोई विशेष स्थान हो, बस कुछ करने की चाहत और खुद पर भरोसा हो,  सफलता एक दिन जरूर मिलती है ।  चलते रहिए , ज़िन्दगी के सफ़र में , क्योंकि चलना ही ज़िन्दगी है ।
Some points for new students -
1. Self study par jyada focus 
2. Jyada se jyada practice 
3. Practice se accuracy aayegi 
4. Jyada accuracy means , examination hall mein paper, kam waqt mein solve

For all competitive exams  :- current affairs, history, geography, hindi, rajasthan gk, indian Constitution & etc

snippet.title: NSW Jewish Board of Deputies
snippet.description:
The NSW Jewish Board of Deputies is the official elected representative roof-body of the Jewish Community in New South Wales, with 61 major communal organisations as its constituents.

The Board leads, speaks and advocates on behalf of the NSW Jewish Community.

Our vision is a united NSW Jewish Community, adequately resourced, enjoying physical and political security as part of a harmonious, inclusive, democratic Australian society. 

To achieve this we consistently perform the following:-

Represent and advocate on behalf of the NSW Jewish Community

Ensure the political and physical security of the NSW Jewish Community.

Combat antisemitism and other forms of racism.

Increase understanding of Israel and its centrality to Jewish life.

Promote social inclusion of all segments of NSW society.

Maintain the unity and cohesion of the NSW Jewish Community.

Ensure continuity of a vibrant NSW Jewish Community.

Hey Tiders! 🌊 I'm the captain behind Topic Tide, where we ride the waves of podcasts to bring you the highlights you crave. 🎙️ Imagine surfing through the vast ocean of 2-4 hour podcasts – a bit overwhelming, right? Topic Tide

snippet.title: Business Standard Hindi
snippet.description:
बिज़नेस स्टैंडर्ड के वीडियो आपके लिए लाते हैं दुनिया भर से अर्थव्यवस्था, व्यवसाय और वित्त (इकॉनमी, बिज़नेस और फाइनेंस) से जुड़े लेटेस्ट अपडेट। 

Business Standard के यूट्यूब चैनल पर आपको मिलेगा हर ताज़ा अपडेट। बिज़नेस की ताजा खबरें देखनी हों, या समाचार, एक्सप्लेनर्स और हमारी खास ‘डीकोडेड’ सीरीज़ के साथ ही एक ही जगह पर आपको मिलेंगे टेक, बैकिंग, फाइनेंस, मार्केट, स्पोर्ट्स और मैन्युफैक्टरिंग सेक्टर्स के एक्सक्लूसिव इंटरव्यू। 
देश भर में हो रहे नीतिगत परिवर्तनों, शेयर बाज़ार और पर्सनल फाइनेंस से जुड़ी अहम खबरों से रहें अपडेट। 
स्टॉक्स, IPO, बाजार के अपडेट और बिज़नेस आइडियाज़ के बारे में रोजाना के अपडेट्स जानने के लिए Like, Share & Subscribe करें हमारा यूट्यूब चैनल। इसी के साथ हमारे चैनल पर आपको मिलेगा महत्वपूर्ण इवेंट्स का पूरा कवरेज, जैसे बजट, सरकारी नीतियों में हुए बदलाव, और दुनिया भर की महत्वपूर्ण खबरें। 
हमारे चैनल के ताजा वीडियो नोटिफिकेशन पाने के लिए बेल आइकन 🔔को प्रेस करना न भूलें ।

snippet.title: Euronews em Português
snippet.description:
Bem-vindo ao canal oficial da Euronews no YouTube!  

A nossa equipa de cerca de 500 jornalistas, de mais de 30 nacionalidades diferentes, traz-lhe notícias com uma perspetiva imparcial a qualquer hora do dia. Vamos além dos títulos, procuramos a vozes da Europa e do mundo. No YouTube encontra os conteúdos originais do canal internacional de notícias líder na Europa.  

A nossa missão é dar às pessoas as chaves para formarem uma opinião. Confiamos na capacidade de decisão individual e procuramos dar ao nosso público a maior diversidade de pontos de vista. Não nos baseamos em preconceitos, mas em factos. Acreditamos que todas as perspetivas são importantes.

A Euronews nasceu da vontade de criar um canal de notícias europeu, independente e forte. Como único canal internacional de notícias com uma perspetiva europeia, é na Euronews que o mundo confia para saber o que a Europa tem a dizer.

Siga-nos nas redes sociais:

A nossa missão é dar às pessoas as chaves para formarem uma opinião. Confiamos na capacidade de decisão individual e procuramos dar ao nosso público a maior diversidade de pontos de vista. Não nos baseamos em preconceitos, mas em factos. Acreditamos que todas as perspetivas são importantes.

A Euronews nasceu da vontade de criar um canal de notícias europeu, independente e forte. Como único canal internacional de notícias com uma perspetiva europeia, é na Euronews que o mundo confia para saber o que a Europa tem a dizer.

snippet.title: Dua Lipa
snippet.description:
The official YouTube channel for Dua Lipa.

Born and raised in London to Kosovar-Albanian parents, Dua Lipa signed to Warner Records in 2015 releasing her self titled debut in 2017 which featured the hit singles, 'Be The One', 'IDGAF', 'Hotter Than Hell' & her first UK #1 hit 'New Rules'. 

Critical success soon followed as Dua Lipa picked up Brit Awards for 'Best Female Solo Artist' and 'Best British Breakthrough Act' as well as Grammy Awards for 'Best New Artist' and 'Best Dance Recording' for the track 'Electricity' in collaboration with Silk City.

Her second internationally acclaimed studio album 'Future Nostalgia' was released in 2020 and included the hit singles 'Don't Start Now, 'Break My Heart', 'Hallucinate' and 'Levitating', with the remix album 'Club Future Nostalgia' following shortly after featuring guest appearances from 'Blackpink', 'Missy Elliott', 'Madonna' and 'Gwen Stefani'.

snippet.title: euronews (in Italiano)
snippet.description:
Benvenuti al canale Youtube ufficiale di Euronews! 

Tutti i giorni, a tutte le ore, la nostra squadra di 500 giornalisti provenienti da oltre 30 Paesi lavora per raccontarvi l'Europa con assoluta imparzialità. Su questo canale trovate una selezione dei migliori contenuti della TV europea per eccellenza. 

La nostra missione è quella di dare alle persone la possibilità di formarsi una propria opinione. Confidiamo nell'intelligenza e nella capacità delle persone di decidere da sole e cerchiamo di fornire al nostro pubblico la più grande diversità di punti di vista attraverso un giornalismo imparziale.
Ci concentriamo su fatti, idee e soluzioni.
Crediamo che tutti i punti di vista siano importanti.

Euronews è nato dalla volontà di creare un canale d'informazione europeo indipendente. Essendo l'unico media internazionale con una prospettiva europea, Euronews è il luogo a cui si rivolge il mondo per ascoltare ciò che l'Europa ha da dire.

snippet.title: Medhavi
snippet.description:
Indore Kautilya Academy Bhopal is the best Coaching for UPSC, MPPSC, SSC, MPSI and GOVERNMENT EXAMS aspirants who want to be an IAS, IPS, IFS, Deputy Collector, DSP and Government Officers.

The study module of the academy is designed in such a way that it trains the candidate not only for administrative services of Union and State Public Service Commission exams like UPSC, MPPSC but also for the lower Subordinate exams like SSC, MPSI, RAILWAY, Samvida Shikshak, Bank PO.

Kautilya Academy Bhopal believes in the success of aspirants and it proved by the academy when this year academy has given the MPPSC 2018 Topper Harshal Choudhary.
The Institute has a highly experienced faculty team lead by Narendra Singh Somvanshi Sir Founder and Director of Kautilya Academy Narendra Singh Somvanshi.

Based in Singapore, CNA covers global developments with an Asian perspective. Come to us not just for the latest news, but also documentaries, expert analysis and stories behind the headlines.

Our correspondents are based in major cities across Asia, including Kuala Lumpur, Jakarta, Bangkok, Tokyo, Seoul and Beijing, as well as in New York, Washington D.C. and London.

Hit the subscribe button to be notified when we upload fresh news clips and documentaries on YouTube, or bookmark cna.asia for the top headlines, insightful reads and more videos.

And tap on the Community tab and tell us what you’d like to see more of! https://cna.asia
